HEADWORD: Race suicide
<hw>Race suicide</hw>. <def>The voluntary failure of the members of a
race or people to have a number of children sufficient to keep the birth
rate equal to the death rate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

